OL,9,FWhat is a "code red"?
OL,11,FThe phrase "code red" was used
OL,12,Frepeatedly in reference to the
OL,13,Fincident at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman, also
OL,14,Fknown locally as Amman Valley School.
OL,16,FWhen staff decided that it was a "code
OL,17,Fred" scenario, announcements were made
OL,18,Fover the PA system and most people
OL,19,Ftook cover in classrooms.
