OL,3,CHow are schools prepared for
OL,4,Cemergencies?
OL,6,FSchools and their local councils are
OL,7,Fresponsible for the specific systems
OL,8,Femployed, and Carmarthenshire County
OL,9,FCouncil opted not to give details as
OL,10,Fto exactly how Amman Valley keeps its
OL,11,Fpupils safe.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Local Government Association
OL,14,Fdeclined to comment on the exact
OL,15,Fsystems in place at schools in Wales
OL,16,Fwhen contacted by ITV News.
