OL,6,FAll education, childcare and
OL,7,Fchildren's social care settings must
OL,8,Fhave emergency plans in place,
OL,9,Faccording to the UK government , but
OL,10,Fthere are no formal requirements in
OL,11,Fterms of what that should include.
OL,13,FA school's emergency plan "should be
OL,14,Fgeneric enough to cover a range of
OL,15,Fpotential incidents", it says,
