OL,3,CHow are schools prepared for
OL,4,Cemergencies?
OL,6,FSchools are expected to use government
OL,7,Fand local council guidance, including
OL,8,Ftemplates and risk assessments, to
OL,9,Fcreate their own safety procedures.
OL,11,FPolice forces work with schools to
OL,12,Fimprove their safety, but the role
OL,13,Fthat they play differs based on local
OL,14,Fneeds and risks, the National Police
OL,15,FChiefs' Council (NPCC) said.
